article.description: Sam Sessoms and Pierre Sarr scored 16 points apiece as Binghamton got past Army 88-73 on Saturday.
article.headline: Sessoms, Sarr carry Binghamton over Army 88-73
article.linkText: Sessoms, Sarr carry Binghamton over Army 88-73
article.story: VESTAL, N.Y. -- Sam Sessoms and Pierre Sarr scored 16 points apiece as Binghamton got past Army 88-73 on Saturday. Sarr also had 13 rebounds and three blocks. Brenton Mills added 15 points and Yarden Willis had 14 points for Binghamton (3-3). Matt Wilson had 22 points and nine rebounds for the Black Knights (2-3). Tommy Funk added 20 points and six assists. Lonnie Grayson had 11 points. Binghamton faces SUNY-Oneonta at home on Tuesday. Army plays Marist on the road next Saturday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
